The following background data on cholera in Ghana were abstracted from the
GIDEON software program:
In recent years, cholera has been reported in Accra, Ashanti, Central,
Upper East, Volta and Western regions.
Year Cases Deaths
1982 1,780
1984 1,015
1991 13,172 409
1992 228 23
1993 1,448 38
1994 2,267 54
1995 4,698 93
1996 1,665 70
1997 379 12
1998 * 123 11
* January to July
